projects.title: Mexo car (Admin Dashboard)
projects.description: Developed a responsive admin dashboard using Flutter Web for Mexo Car, a mobile-based e-commerce application. The web dashboard empowers administrators with intuitive controls for efficient content management, product administration, order monitoring, and user management. Team work project, I worked on creating UI, handle requests from API, building logic using Bloc stage- management.

projects.title: App Shark
projects.description: App Shark is a powerful tool that helps you discover apps installed on your device and analyze the evidence they've been identified for. The app lets you see if apps use technologies like Flutter, React, Xamarin, Ionic, and Native. It provides detailed information about the tools and technologies developers use, giving you a great insight into how the apps you use every day are developed. Discover the latest apps and the most useful information about most apps.

projects.title: Ms  Jacob And Partners
projects.description: Jacob & Partners is a premium investment insights app designed for a select group of members who are passionate about making informed investment decisions. Our app delivers exclusive reports, expert analysis, and up-to-date news on the best investment opportunities across various sectors. Users can engage with the content by sharing their thoughts, reacting to reports, and participating in discussions with like-minded investors. Whether you're a seasoned investor or just getting started, Jacob & Partners provides the tools and information you need to make smart investment choices
